{"tid":862490,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"內褲濕濕！6種分泌物顏色看出警訊「小心黃綠色」","createTime":"2018-10-15T00:53:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-15T11:06:33.000Z","uid":32511,"like":15,"dislike":273,"uniUserReply":63,"replies":[{"pid":"3629304d64cb2621e9d5e2bdd79c00195e2efd84","tid":862490,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T00:53:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/15/003455_7a5eea2bb04b5cd1a455228035818260.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F15%2F003455_7a5eea2bb04b5cd1a455228035818260.png&h=19409e32&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/15/003456_9c36bb5cc5923c8ec6edb07d200e80ca.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F15%2F003456_9c36bb5cc5923c8ec6edb07d200e80ca.png&h=6538258f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n女生常常會被搔癢異味、分泌物過多所擾，如果白帶分泌濕濕黏黏的過多，一整天下來讓人難以忍受。國外女性健康網站就指出，從這6種分泌物狀態就能看出身體的健康狀態，尤其指出分泌物若是黃綠色，就代表可能感染淋病。<br />\n <br />\n國外女性健康網站《Women's Health》報導，整理出以下6種不同的分泌物顏色，來看出其代表身體的健康狀態。<br />\n <br />\n <br />\n1. 透明、白色濕黏分泌物<br />\n <br />\n這代表身體處於「排卵期」，這是你的身體為了讓精子能順利進入陰道與卵子結合，所產生的分泌物，這些黏液就像蛋清一樣。<br />\n <br />\n <br />\n2. 白色、塊狀分泌物，伴隨發癢狀況<br />\n <br />\n可能是「白色念珠菌」（陰道酵母菌的一種）所引起的感染，容易讓下體產生搔癢的症狀。這時分泌物會呈現白色奶酪質地的結塊，且外陰也會出現腫脹的情形。此症狀通常出現在潮濕環境，建議可以使用非處方的抗真菌藥物。<br />\n <br />\n <br />\n3.黃綠色分泌物、下體刺痛<br />\n <br />\n如果私處分泌物呈現黃綠色，並伴隨刺痛感、排尿灼熱等症狀，就要小心可能是感染淋病（gonorrhea）、砂眼衣原體（chlamydia）細菌型性病。淋病菌可經由性行為口交傳染他人，因此建議性伴侶雙方都到醫院檢查。<br />\n <br />\n <br />\n4. 分泌物呈現灰色、而且有強烈味道<br />\n <br />\n感染「細菌性陰道炎」會產生強烈的魚腥味，15到44歲的女性最常出現感染，這代表陰道中的細菌失衡。<br />\n <br />\n <br />\n5. 分泌物呈現灰綠色、泡沫狀<br />\n <br />\n內褲飄出陣陣難聞的意味，又出現頻尿、陰道搔癢的情形，則可能是感染「滴蟲性陰道炎（trichomoniasis）。該症狀會透過性行為、共用毛巾、貼身衣物、浴缸等途徑傳染，且不論男女都可能被感染。<br />\n <br />\n <br />\n6. 分泌物是粉紅色，帶紅色或棕色<br />\n <br />\n月經周期時殘留的血絲與「子宮內膜出血」會讓分泌物變成粉色或咖啡色，通常在女性剛生產後的幾個月較容易出現是正常的，因為她的身體還在調整荷爾蒙。但如果持續發現分泌物褐色斑點情況時，還是建議看醫生檢查，要注意是否為子宮頸癌會卵巢癌的警訊。"},{"pid":"11602534b90c121b29e801ec460ae53376b5ec4a","tid":862490,"uid":3302,"like":261,"dislike":5,"score":256,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T00:54:08.000Z","msg":"嘩 屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c82d79a6505125edbab12a0aec847b17360f8e3","tid":862490,"uid":21423,"like":130,"dislike":15,"score":115,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T00:55:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8fe433f4575f0881553c0acbd1ccd63b7df37958","tid":862490,"uid":29080,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T01:04:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/thumb/7/70/Police_Magazine.jpg/300px-Police_Magazine.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fthumb%2F7%2F70%2FPolice_Magazine.jpg%2F300px-Police_Magazine.jpg&h=95240658&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f61fdb5ae14bc6ab89ca3e78593f04f579b4233b","tid":862490,"uid":38777,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T01:15:25.000Z","msg":"屌...<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e8989380d5daeb8b207368a52315f9a6fca20aa","tid":862490,"uid":196310,"like":0,"dislike":15,"score":-15,"quote":{"pid":"2c82d79a6505125edbab12a0aec847b17360f8e3","tid":862490,"uid":21423,"like":130,"dislike":15,"score":115,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T00:55:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T01:18:31.000Z","msg":"😱😱😱"},{"pid":"6d02ce2474ba437d8c8ca9741e7cf4056829c997","tid":862490,"uid":210638,"like":10,"dislike":5,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T01:18:43.000Z","msg":"抹茶味奶酪雪糕<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb05b8f93813352a6df40bea337db033619ff3a8","tid":862490,"uid":63859,"like":151,"dislike":1,"score":150,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T01:20:11.000Z","msg":"嘩 屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢啲就咁撚大張圖"},{"pid":"960de345ba06d9aee0da8548d883c69b6b718a9d","tid":862490,"uid":40397,"like":23,"dislike":2,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T01:33:06.000Z","msg":"好似傷風D鼻涕咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"361ce4a77ad72889e1b14aaf49c26a0355bdc26a","tid":862490,"uid":119778,"like":9,"dislike":10,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T01:35:39.000Z","msg":"想奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47a3dc053b3cc7920a96f298fb2167aa4c449b08","tid":862490,"uid":213877,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"361ce4a77ad72889e1b14aaf49c26a0355bdc26a","tid":862490,"uid":119778,"like":9,"dislike":10,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T01:35:39.000Z","msg":"想奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T01:38:09.000Z","msg":"識貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faa709aa899a1603838b5c56fca237fd4d58b1f6","tid":862490,"uid":55458,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T01:53:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29f5c043d63d7b201946d526b125bb1908f3a028","tid":862490,"uid":26953,"like":205,"dislike":1,"score":204,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T01:55:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/15/095516_e8c578a0add50618fa479bfb596a889d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F15%2F095516_e8c578a0add50618fa479bfb596a889d.png&h=7cd4ed1c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6bef4f435e331e95401cb6f4c9e4db795e55410e","tid":862490,"uid":35430,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018