,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T06:51:01.000Z","msg":"4. 分泌物呈現灰色、而且有強烈味道<br />\n<br />\n感染「細菌性陰道炎」會產生強烈的魚腥味，15到44歲的女性最常出現感染，這代表陰道中的細菌失衡。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n5. 分泌物呈現灰綠色、泡沫狀<br />\n<br />\n內褲飄出陣陣難聞的意味，又出現頻尿、陰道搔癢的情形，則可能是感染「滴蟲性陰道炎（trichomoniasis）。該症狀會透過性行為、共用毛巾、貼身衣物、浴缸等途徑傳染，且不論男女都可能被感染<br />\n<br />\n仆街, 睇埋張圖, 想嘔"},{"pid":"cbed9ef88593c357ceb1f0d5273489cc11d96142","tid":862490,"uid":71913,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T06:51:52.000Z","msg":"睇完都係覺得做男人好<br />\n<br />\n靚仔靚女一樣有著數<br />\n<br />\n但做仔唔洗煩"},{"pid":"2322907205c35abc8de71cebec11c6130bfefbb0","tid":862490,"uid":51532,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T06:53:13.000Z","msg":"下次貼底褲就得，呢家搞到個心好唔舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9650c563af7ef139f2a9713699eedc28711c917","tid":862490,"uid":178800,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T06:56:05.000Z","msg":"到底咩女人先會咁樣黃綠色?!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌,睇完呢張相我3日打唔到飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0067e63a784469350277d0557f22800c1f719540","tid":862490,"uid":13850,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T07:02:05.000Z","msg":"似感冒既鼻涕多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e77579048e98095ad5e412594094f42d8f9cea14","tid":862490,"uid":34168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T07:04:47.000Z","msg":"加個慎入上去啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class